        "description": {
            "value": "<p>Granted by @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.Tiger Stance]{Tiger Stance}</p>\n<p>You enter the stance of a tiger and can make tiger claw attacks. These deal 1d8 slashing damage; are in the brawling group; and have the agile, finesse, nonlethal, and unarmed traits.</p>\n<p>On a critical success with your tiger claws, if you deal damage, the target takes @Localize[PF2E.PersistentDamage.Bleed1d4.success].</p>\n<p>As long as your Speed is at least 20 feet while in Tiger Stance, you can Step 10 feet.</p>"
